<h3 id="vue2-源码中的数据劫持" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#vue2-源码中的数据劫持" aria-hidden="true">#</a> vue2 源码中的数据劫持</h3>
<div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre v-pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token comment">// src/core/instance/observer/index.js</span>
